            "body": "Thought about this a bit more. What we need to do is separate createClient into two function : \r\n\r\n- handshakeClient(client), which does all the necessary steps to transition from HANDSHAKE to PLAY states\r\n- createClient(), which creates a TCP connection and passes it to handshakeClient.\r\n\r\nThis way, people who want to use any other kind of stream (a File stream for protocol analysis, or a proxy stream) are able to do so without difficulty. ",
